{"lemma":"عَجَلَةُ","slug":"عَجَلَةُ","root":"ع.ج.ل","root_slug":"ع-ج-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ج-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":8},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28193","n28201","n28202","n28203"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of عَجِلَ (ʕajila) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"haste, hurry, speed, speediness, celerity","examples":[{"text":"أَنَا عَلَى عَجَلَةٍ.","english":"I'm in a hurry"},{"text":"فِي ٱلتَّأَنِّي ٱلسَّلَامَةُ، وَفِي ٱلْعَجَلَةِ ٱلنَّدَامَةُ.","english":"Sedateness brings welfare, hurry brings regret."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"wheel"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"precipitation, precipitance"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of عِجْل (ʕijl, “calf”)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"female calf; heifer (rare, for female calves are also called عِجْل)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"Halopyrum mucronatum"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"feminine singular of عَجِل (ʕajil)","tags":["feminine","form-of","singular"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"At least for the abstract senses, verbal noun of عَجِلَ (ʕajila, “to hurry”).\nCompare also Hebrew עגלה (agalá, “carriage, cart”) and Hebrew מַעְגָּל (ma'agál, “circle”)\n\nFrom عِجْل (ʕijl) + ـَة (-a)."},"ipa":["/ʕa.d͡ʒa.la/","/ʕi.d͡ʒa.la/","/ʕa.d͡ʒi.la/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28193","headword_ar":"عجّلهُ","root":"Ejl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEojiylN","text_ar":"تَعْجِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 4, in two places. ―         -b2-  [It generally relates to some inanimate object.] It is said in the Kur [xxxviii. 15],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rab~anaA Eaj~ilo lanaA","text_ar":"رَبَّنَا عَجِّلْ لَنَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiT~anaA qabola yawomi AlHisaAbi","text_ar":"قِطَّنَا قَبْلَ يَوْمِ الحِسَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"O our Lord hasten to us our portion before the day of reckoning"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) accord. to some,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"our portion of punishment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but accord. to Sa'eed Ibn-Jubeyr, it means,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of Paradise."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qT","text_ar":"قط"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaj~alotu A_ilayohi","text_ar":"عَجَّلْتُ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaAla","text_ar":"المَالَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I brought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conveyed, hastily,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speedily, to him the property;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hastened its coming to him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaj~alotu lahu mina Alv~amani ka*aA","text_ar":"عَجَّلْتُ لَهُ مِنَ الثَّمَنِ كَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I paid him in advance, of the price, such a sum."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaj~alahu mina AlkiraA='i ka*aA","text_ar":"عَجَّلَهُ مِنَ الكِرَا=ءِ كَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave him in ready money,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"promptly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quickly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in advance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the hire, such a sum."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaj~ala lahu Alv~amana","text_ar":"عَجَّلَ لَهُ الثَّمَنَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave to him"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in ready money,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"promptly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quickly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in advance, the price"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ej~l naqodahu","text_ar":"عجّل نَقْدَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He paid it in ready money, promptly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quickly"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (ISk, S and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zkA^","text_ar":"زكا"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biEotuhu taEojiylFA bitaEojiylK","text_ar":"بِعْتُهُ تَعْجِيلًا بِتَعْجِيلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I sold it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I sold to him, present,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ready,"},{"kind":"text","text":"merchandise,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for present,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ready,"},{"kind":"text","text":"money]. (S voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAjizN","text_ar":"نَاجِزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaj~alotu All~aHoma","text_ar":"عَجَّلْتُ اللَّحْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) inf. n. as above, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I cooked the flesh-meat in haste."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lawo Eaj~alota biA^ay~imika AlEajuwla","text_ar":"لَوْ عَجَّلْتَ بِاَيِّمِكَ العَجُولَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", a prov., [which, app., is properly rendered"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Would that thou didst hasten, with thy husbandless woman, the early portion of food called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eajuwl","text_ar":"عَجُول"},{"kind":"text","text":", or the right reading may be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEij~awola","text_ar":"العِجَّوْلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaj~ilo bihaA","text_ar":"عَجِّلْ بِهَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alz~awaAja","text_ar":"الزَّوَاجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hasten thou, with her,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with thy husbandless woman, marriage"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) One says also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaj~alotumo","text_ar":"عَجَّلْتُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lah~anotumo","text_ar":"لَهَّنْتُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ye supplied,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fed, with the early portion of food called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luhonap","text_ar":"لُهْنَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; which is also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eajuwl","text_ar":"عَجُول"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eij~awol","text_ar":"عِجَّوْل"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c.]. (S, TA. [For"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lah~anotumo","text_ar":"لَهَّنْتُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", Golius appears to have read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lah~ayotumo","text_ar":"لَهَّيْتُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is evidently wrong.]) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ej~l A^aqiTahu","text_ar":"عجّل اَقِطَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tEj~lhu","text_ar":"تعجّلهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made his"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"preparation of dried curd called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AqT","text_ar":"اقط"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into what are termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajaAjiyl","text_ar":"عَجَاجِيل"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euj~aAlN","text_ar":"عُجَّالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaj~alotu A^aqiTiY EajaAjiyla","text_ar":"عَجَّلْتُ اَقِطِى عَجَاجِيلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I made my"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AqT","text_ar":"اقط"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EjAjyl","text_ar":"عجاجيل"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O.)       -A2-  See also 1, first sentence."}],"source_refs":["TA","S","O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n28201","headword_ar":"عُجْلَةٌ","root":"Ejl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EujaAlapN","text_ar":"عُجَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n28202","headword_ar":"عِجْلَةٌ","root":"Ejl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"fem. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EijolN","text_ar":"عِجْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (Abu-l-Jarráh, S, O, Msb.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A water-skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skin for water"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for milk;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siqaA='N","text_ar":"سِقَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, O, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EijalN","text_ar":"عِجَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EijaAlN","text_ar":"عِجَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"water-wheel such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duwlaAb","text_ar":"دُولَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IAar, O, K: [see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajalapN","text_ar":"عَجَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) pls. as above. (K.)       -A3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A species of plant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which extends along the ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa$iyjN","text_ar":"وَشِيجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: (O, TA:) AHn says of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w$yj","text_ar":"وشيج"},{"kind":"text","text":", on the authority of Aboo-Ziyád,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it grows, at first, from one root, then branches forth upon the surface of the earth, in innumerable branches, every branch having a knot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"joint,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaEobN","text_ar":"كَعْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from which knot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"joint, grow other branches; it cleaves to the ground, not rising high; its leaves are like"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1965},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"those of wheat; and while green, it is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eijolap","text_ar":"عِجْلَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (O;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and it is the best of pasture, and is not"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baqol","text_ar":"بَقْل"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O, TA:) and it is said to be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a tree having leaves and joints,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"knots,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kuEuwb","text_ar":"كُعُوب"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and pliant canes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qDb","text_ar":"قضب"},{"kind":"text","text":"in my original, I read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSab","text_ar":"قَصَب"},{"kind":"text","text":", (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa$iyjN","text_ar":"وَشِيجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"long,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elongated, with a fruit like the foot of the domestic fowl, contracted, which, when it dries up, opens; and not having any blossom."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EijaAlapN","text_ar":"عِجَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n28203","headword_ar":"عَجَلَةٌ","root":"Ejl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajalN","text_ar":"عَجَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", first sentence.       -A2-  Also ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cart,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wheeled carriage of any kind;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=lap","text_ar":"ا=لَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=lapu HamolK","text_ar":"ا=لَةُ حَمْلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"instrument of carriage"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is drawn along by the bull:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) said by Er-Rághib to be so called because of the quickness of its passing along: (TA:) pl. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajalN","text_ar":"عَجَلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or rather this is a coll. gen. n.] and [pl. of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEojaAlN","text_ar":"اَعْجَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K) and [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EijaAlN","text_ar":"عِجَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pieces of wood constructed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece of wood,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing that is constructed like the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"women's camel-vehicle called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miHaf~ap","text_ar":"مِحَفَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon which burdens are carried:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, * K:) pl. [or coll. gen. n.] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajalN","text_ar":"عَجَلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh, Msb.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"water-wheel such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manojanuwn","text_ar":"مَنْجَنُون"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duwlaAb","text_ar":"دُولَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon which water is drawn:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O: [see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EijolapN","text_ar":"عِجْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaAlapN","text_ar":"مَحَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"great sheave of a pulley by means of which camels draw water"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K:) pl. [or coll. gen. n.] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajalN","text_ar":"عَجَلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece of wood lying transversely,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"horizontally, upon the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEaAmap","text_ar":"نَعَامَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or rather"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEaAmataAni","text_ar":"نَعَامَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two posts"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the well, to which the large bucket is suspended:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Kilábee, S, O, K: [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuronuwqN","text_ar":"زُرْنُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) pl. [or coll. gen. n.] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajalN","text_ar":"عَجَلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A kind of ladder made from a palm-tree, like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naqiyr","text_ar":"نَقِير"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is the trunk of a palm-tree hollowed, and having the like of steps made in it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"mentioned in a trad. as the means of ascending to an upper chamber. (O.) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leathern vessel for water such as is called an"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_idaAwap","text_ar":"اـِدَاوَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": and some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leathern water-bag such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mazaAdap","text_ar":"مَزَادَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b7-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaArapu vawobK","text_ar":"كَارَةُ ثَوْبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A garment made up into a bundle"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EijaAlN","text_ar":"عِجَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEojaAlN","text_ar":"اَعْجَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", by the rejection of the augmentative ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sing.]. (TA.) ―         -b8-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A rock"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is as though"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"growing forth by itself upon rugged, elevated, hard ground."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, O.) ―         -b9-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajalN","text_ar":"عَجَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", latter half."}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA","Msb","Mgh"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}